{"id":69901,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/05/人类历史简画：战争、女人、性欲和阴谋/","date":"2010-05-11T10:02:48Z","modified":"2010-05-11T10:02:48Z","title":"人类历史简画：战争、女人、性欲和阴谋","content":"<p>原作者：<br />来源<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://obviousmag.org/en/archives/2007/04/brief_illustrated_history_of_mankind.html\">brief illustrated history of mankind</a><br />译者<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/148972\">Lio Joslin</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://blog.uncovering.org/archives/uploads/2007/2007041100_breve_historia_humanidade-tm.jpg\" alt=\" Brief History Humanity Humour Pictures War Sex Intrigue Church Religion \"></p>\n<p>什么？你是历史教师？哼，这幅画可比你讲的多得多。不信？等着瞧吧，才不只这么点呢。复杂多样的人类历史长河波澜壮阔，集中于这小小卷轴之中，而且不乏细节，这个真不可能。但是，请细看——人类历史简画。</p>\n<p>在我看来，这幅画非同寻常的有意思，基于两个原因：</p>\n<p>——我从来没有看到如此精彩的人类史画卷；</p>\n<p>——我想我看得到推动人类史进程的四大因素: 战争、女人、性欲和阴谋，周而复始。</p>\n<p>……哦！天啊，那个人，怎么会是我？</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://blog.uncovering.org/archives/uploads/2007/2007041101_breve_historia_humanidade-1-tm.jpg\" alt=\" Brief History Humanity Humour Pictures War Sex Intrigue Church Religion \"></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/148972/104609#newComment\">添加新评论</a></p>\n<p><strong>相关文章：</strong></p>\n<p> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://article.yeeyan.org/view/130622/85036?from=rss_related\">[看图说话]——海地地震明星捐款榜</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/364558459/yeeyan/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://article.yeeyan.org/view/148972/104609\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\"></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/yeeyan/364558459/art01.html\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/yeeyan/364558459/art01.gif\"></a></p>\n","author":880,"categories":[20534],"tags":[9040]}